# Patterns DVC must ignore. Learn more: https://dvc.org/doc/user-guide/dvcignore
#
# GUARDRAIL: the open-data CSVs are the project's deliverable and stay versioned
# in git (directly downloadable, no DVC/S3 needed). Keep them out of DVC so a
# stray `dvc add data/` never moves them out of git.
data/*.csv
data/**/*.csv
